- create a barrier and outline for your textboxs (fieldbox element)
-legend element allows you to name your fieldbox


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head> </head>
<body>
<form>
   <fieldset>
   <legend> Enter title: </legend>
 enter paragraph:
    <input type="date" name="displayed text">
    Number of days: <input type="number" name="displayed text" min="number" max="number"
<br> <br>
 name: <input type="text">
    </fieldset>
</form>
</body>
</html>
